Veteran Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie’s first wife has reacted to news of his second wife and son.
Yul’s wife, May has birthed four children for him. Three of his children are boys and the first child is a 17 years old girl who is currently in the university.
Yul went ahead to pay his second wife’s bride price after she gave birth to another son for him.
The actor made the announcement via his official Instagram page, in the post he shared pictures of his baby boy and stated that he loves the boy as much as he loves his other kids.
He also announced that he is now married to the mother of his son, a co actress, Judy Austin. Yul and Judy met on a movie set, he plays the role of her director while she produces movies for him.
In the comments section of the official announcement post Yul made, his first wife, May shared her reaction to the development in 5 simple words.
May wrote, “May God judge you both”.
Other celebrities had their opinions of the matter and shared it in the comments. Some congratulated Yul, while the rest showed remorse for the first wife.



